text: Gumbazy () is a rural locality (a village) in Sterlibashevsky Selsoviet, Sterlibashevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 27 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 4 km from Sterlibashevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlibashevsky District
title: Gumbazy
